        Chatbot tÆ° váº¥n giÃ y
        <span id="chat-close" style="cursor:pointer; font-size:20px;">Ã—</span>
    </div>
    <div id="chatbox"></div>
    <div class="chat-input">
        <input id="txtMessage" type="text" placeholder="Nháº­p cÃ¢u há»i...">
        <button id="btnSend">Gá»­i</button>
